Package scotty.template

This package contains the template related code for Scotty.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Tokens
    Scotty template tokens
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CharQueue
    A fixed size character buffer that overflows into an output source if provided.
    Parser
    Parses Scotty templates, applies data from the Database considering the given context, and produces transformed output.
